text: ยง 13-183 State supervision. The retirement system shall be subject to the supervision of the department of insurance in accordance with the provisions of sections three hundred seven, three hundred eight, three hundred nine, three hundred ten, three hundred eleven and three hundred twelve of the insurance law, so far as the same are applicable thereto, and are not inconsistent with the provisions of this chapter.

chapter.text: NEW YORK CITY EMPLOYEES' RETIREMENT SYSTEM
